<br>
So, I am gonna go with the camp of thought that any item will require the gems, or coffins or what have you.  I hope at least one person can learn from my mistake =)<br>
<br>
still, it has some limited use.  no-mana ac/regen clicky effect is still thx...towards the end game more, as my style is, if I am 00m, it is not a time where any ac/regen buff is gonna help me, mana-free or not haha.<br>
<br>
